I have been trying to prepare the package to be go-gettable but since the *.pb.go files have to be generated,

What about checking the generated go files in? In the Google Cloud API packages, that's what we do (e.g. https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/gcloud-golang/tree/master/bigtable/internal/cluster_data_proto).
